10:36
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='625000' id='t-625000'>This is an experiment, really, for a client, Quicksilver,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='628000' id='t-628000'>where we were taking what was a six-shot sequence</span>
