<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='634000' id='t-634000'>So, this is a six-shot sequence.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='636000' id='t-636000'>I've taken one shot; I cropped it a few different ways.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='640000' id='t-640000'>And then the tiny line of copy says,</span>
