<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='657000' id='t-657000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='660000' id='t-660000'>I don't have the site. It's just the piece itself.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
