<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702000' id='t-702000'>And it was purposely done to look fairly serious.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='705000' id='t-705000'>It wasn't some, you know, weird grunge type or something;</span>
