<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='711000' id='t-711000'>Poster for Atlantic Center for the Arts, a school in Florida.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:05
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='714000' id='t-714000'>This amazes me. This is a product I just found out.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='717000' id='t-717000'>I was in the Caribbean at Christmas,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='719000' id='t-719000'>and I'm just blown away that in this day and age they will still sell --</span>
